1.1.name: wordpress/picasaedissimo
1.1.description:
Picasaedissimo is a plugin to display the latest or random images from a selected Picasa Webalbum RSS feed in your sidebar.

This is a modified version of the Picasaed plugin by Jon Link, since his stopped working and it seems he stopped developing it.

For comments and suggestions drop by at http://www.gofloripa.net.
